If you claim your WL spot on Blocksmith, you will receive 1 "guaranteed mint pass token" AND 1 "FCFS mint pass token". The mint will happen in three phases, described below:

Phase 1 - During this phase, you will only be able to mint using 1 SOL plus a "guaranteed mint pass token" per mint. Since there will be 5000 or less of these "guaranteed" mint pass tokens sent out, you will be guaranteed to be able to mint a Gemmy NFT during this phase if you hold one of these mint pass tokens and the required 1 SOL.

Phase 2 - During this phase, you will only be able to mint using 1 SOL plus a "FCFS mint pass token" per mint. Any Gemmys that were not minted during Phase 1 will be available to mint during this phase. Since there will be more FCFS mint pass tokens than remaining unminted Gemmys, this phase will be FCFS (first come, first served).

Phase 3 - Public mint. Any Gemmys not minted during Phase 1 and 2 will be available for public mint.
